To join The Future of Fixing wiki, submit a request to the wiki organizers.

=<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">Welcome to the resource site for //The Future of Fixing//, an exhibition and programme about attitudes to repair.</span>= 
<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">This is an open source exhibition: all the materials are freely available for you to download and do it yourself. This wiki site allows anyone to make their own version of the exhibition, with everything you need from sample exhibit lists, reading lists, texts, templates and captions. </span>
<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">Become a member of this wiki to tell us what you've done with it.</span>
<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">You'll be able to log it in our network section so others can pick up and learn from what you created.</span>